Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:19.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I’m wishing you never let go of me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:23.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君に届く日がくること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:30.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I’m running with the love that we're destined for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:35.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと
